author: Tabatha
title: Tabatha
text: The products are really good and there's a large variety. Products are fairly priced. I order mostly through the website which is easy to use, but I've also visited the store and everyone I dealt with was very knowledgeable, helpful and friendly. I have, and will continue to recommend them to anyone looking for vaping needs.
